{"id":656981,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/10/【立此存照】请使用：祝愿我祖国繁荣昌盛人民幸/","date":"2020-10-02T09:48:17Z","modified":"2020-10-02T15:15:05Z","title":"【立此存照】请使用：祝愿祖国繁荣昌盛人民幸福安康等话术","content":"<p>10月1日，人民日报发布了一条“《国家2020》用歌声为祖国送祝福”的新浪微博，从评论区的转发可以看到有大量微博大V参与了此消息的转发，格式统一，甚至内文一致。<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-656991\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/1068-izwfpyt2654918.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"313\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/1068-izwfpyt2654918.jpg 591w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/1068-izwfpyt2654918-300x209.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-656995\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/a953-izwfpyt2654924.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"364\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/a953-izwfpyt2654924.jpg 364w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/a953-izwfpyt2654924-228x300.jpg 228w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 364px) 100vw, 364px\" /></p>\n<p>男子团体组合R1SE成员赵让也转发了这条微博，然而微博文案却意外“翻车”，赵让这条微博如此写道：</p>\n<blockquote><p># 我爱我的国 我爱我的家#  祝愿我们的祖国繁荣昌盛，人民幸福安康<strong>等话术</strong></p></blockquote>\n<p>微博末尾疑似忘记删除原通稿“等话术”三个关键字，引发了网民关注，成为了又一起<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%A7%E6%A6%828%E7%82%B920%E5%88%86%E5%8F%91\">“大概八点二十分发”</a>事件，这些显示出中共官方或娱乐经纪公司对于明星转发“国庆爱国帖文”有着统一的要求，是一种自上而下的安排。</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-656994\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/42f0-izwfpyt2654930.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/42f0-izwfpyt2654930.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/42f0-izwfpyt2654930-275x300.jpg 275w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></p>\n<blockquote><p>@big_ear_cat：爱国连自己打几句话都懒得动，复制粘贴结果搞成八点二十分发事件了。</p>\n<p>@流量大咖邱少华 ：赵让是不是没读过书啊。</p>\n<p>@jerry16789：自动“爱国”机，懒人的无脑舔。</p>\n<p>@idzhang3：毕竟也算明星也是为了爱国，大家都原谅了。</p>\n\n\t\t<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 50%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-656981 gallery-columns-2 gallery-size-large'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/10/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e8%af%b7%e4%bd%bf%e7%94%a8%ef%bc%9a%e7%a5%9d%e6%84%bf%e6%88%91%e7%a5%96%e5%9b%bd%e7%b9%81%e8%8d%a3%e6%98%8c%e7%9b%9b%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e5%b9%b8/ejr6smtxyaa-hel/'><img width=\"485\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EjR6SMTXYAA-heL-485x1024.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EjR6SMTXYAA-heL-485x1024.jpeg 485w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EjR6SMTXYAA-heL-142x300.jpeg 142w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EjR6SMTXYAA-heL.jpeg 568w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 485px) 100vw, 485px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/10/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e8%af%b7%e4%bd%bf%e7%94%a8%ef%bc%9a%e7%a5%9d%e6%84%bf%e6%88%91%e7%a5%96%e5%9b%bd%e7%b9%81%e8%8d%a3%e6%98%8c%e7%9b%9b%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e5%b9%b8/ejr6sw2waaaegoq/'><img width=\"485\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EjR6SW2WAAAEgoQ-485x1024.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EjR6SW2WAAAEgoQ-485x1024.jpeg 485w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EjR6SW2WAAAEgoQ-142x300.jpeg 142w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EjR6SW2WAAAEgoQ.jpeg 568w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 485px) 100vw, 485px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" />\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p>@WongChakLui2：拿iphone去發就已經不愛國了。</p></blockquote>\n","author":1069,"categories":[18271,38827,41492,38912,40210,39486],"tags":[8635,10588,9465,9481,25859,42120]}